{"tid":1646332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(通知美國議員)提供盜版直播 內地影音平台:讓NBA賺不到錢","createTime":"2019-10-11T09:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T11:32:04.000Z","uid":171506,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9eddc074f7c99bc1bcbdd0e2483ccc685a4d16d3","tid":1646332,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:10:47.000Z","msg":"美國職籃(NBA)因「撐港言論自由」風波遭中國媒體圍剿，NBA季前賽(中國賽)湖人隊對陣籃網隊的比賽昨晚如期在上海登場，央視、騰訊表明不會在電視和網絡轉播。<br />\n<br />\n據中央社報道，有內網路影音平台提供盜版連結，並註明「籃球無國界，但是我們有國家，從此不可能再為NBA花一分錢。免費看所有NBA視頻，喜歡籃球的小夥伴們趕快前來下載」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，有平台表明堅決維護國家主權和領土完整，為此提供盜版的NBA賽事直播源，強調「讓NBA一毛錢也賺不到」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2273342/%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%9B%9C%E7%89%88%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD+%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%B3%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%3A%E8%AE%93NBA%E8%B3%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E9%8C%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2273342%2F%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BE%259B%25E7%259B%259C%25E7%2589%2588%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD%2B%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25B3%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%258F%25B0%253A%25E8%25AE%2593NBA%25E8%25B3%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%258C%25A2&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwch5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=cfbc4a20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2273342/%E6%8F%90%E4%BE%9B%E7%9B%9C%E7%89%88%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD+%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%B3%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%3A%E8%AE%93NBA%E8%B3%BA%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0%E9%8C%A2</a>"},{"pid":"d49818e3849dd10d93ab16e14346510748d9c401","tid":1646332,"uid":82253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T09:46:24.000Z","msg":"聲援NBA 一齊打籃球<br />\n籃球活動：1025-26#StandWithMorey榮光盃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1646298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1646298</a>"},{"pid":"b1ed075e3d13d0720611809f2a36a8a3ccab5bfb","tid":1646332,"uid":291626,"like":1,"dislike":